<a name="module_ProductDBPlugins"></a>

The ProductDBPlugins module consists of all the plugins in the meeting. It has 2 maps:
- `all`: Consists of all the plugins in the meeting.
- `active`: Consists of the plugins that are currently in use.


* [ProductDBPlugins](#module_ProductDBPlugins)
    * [.all](#module_ProductDBPlugins+all)
    * [.active](#module_ProductDBPlugins+active)

<a name="module_ProductDBPlugins+all"></a>

### plugins.all
All plugins accessible by the current user.

<a name="module_ProductDBPlugins+active"></a>

### plugins.active
All plugins that are currently enabled in the room.
